ca.ualberta.moodroid.repository

Interface RepositoryInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseRepository, FollowRequestRepository, MoodEventRepository, MoodRepository, UserRepository

    public interface RepositoryInterface
    The interface that must be adhered to in order to create a repository, a repository handles the ability to fetch, update, create, and delete data.
    Version:
    v1
    Author:
    Taylor Christie
